# Lychee link checker - exclude URLs that 404 or are not yet available
# https://lychee.cli.rs/recipes/excluding-links

# GitHub Discussions (may not be enabled for repo)
https://github.com/stuchain/CuePoint/discussions

# GitHub Pages (may not be published yet)
https://stuchain.github.io/CuePoint/

# Microsoft docs (page moved or removed)
https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/win_cert/code-signing

# GitHub docs (can return 503 Service Unavailable transiently in CI)
https://docs.github.com/en/code-security/dependabot

# GitHub blob links (may 404 when default branch differs; use relative links instead)
https://github.com/stuchain/CuePoint/blob/main/
https://github.com/StuChain/CuePoint/blob/main/

# File links that lychee fails to resolve (paths exist; workaround for lychee path resolution)
file://.*/docs/release/changelog\.md
file://.*/docs/policy/telemetry\.md
file://.*/docs/release/link
file://.*/docs/security/Security_Incident_Response\.md
file://.*/docs/operations/Release/
